description:
Since March 2020 we have been in lockdown. Without the essential workers who bravely continue to get their job done, our life would be miserable. In this video, on behalf of ALL Seventh-day Adventists around the world, we want to thank every essential worker. 

If you are one of them, THANK YOU. Thank you, bakers, firefighters, doctors, nurses, technologists, farmers, delivery drivers, journalists, therapists, and all others.
#youAreNotAlone
